Facebook-Cleaner
Chrome Extension to remove those bloody suggestion boxes.
Project Page: http://github.com/balupton/Facebook-Cleaner

Installation:
1. Go to the project page at http://github.com/balupton/Facebook-Cleaner
2. Click "Download Source" at the top right
3. Once downloaded, drag "facebook-cleaner.crx" onto an instance of your "Google Chrome" browser.
4. Down the bottom you may have a warning, click continue.
5. Click install on the new extension dialog.
6. You have now installed this extension!